.
├── when availableCreditLimit == 0:
│   └── the nonce of the proposer should be revoked
└── when availableCreditLimit != 0:
    ├── given when the credit used + credit amount exceeds the limit:
    │   └── it should revert
    └── given when the credit used + credit amount is less than, or equal to, the limit:
        ├── given when the credit amount is less than the minimum percentage amount:
        │   └── it should revert
        └── given when the credit amount is greater than, or equal to, the minimum percentage amount:
            ├── the credit used should be incremented by the credit amount
            └── given when the credit used is greater than the upper credit limit threshold:
                └── the nonce of the proposer should be revoked